
{{alias}}( [out,] a, b )
    Perform multiplication of two unsigned 32-bit integers and return an array of two
    unsigned 32-bit integers which represents their 64-bit unsigned integer product.

    Parameters
    ----------
    out: array (optional)
        The output array.

    a: integer
        Unsigned 32-bit integer.

    b: integer
        Unsigned 32-bit integer.

    Returns
    -------
    out: array
        Product.

    Examples
    --------
    > var v = {{alias}}( 1, 10 )
    [ 0, 10 ]
